Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.17,0:00:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.51,0:00:34.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:34.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.30,0:00:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:49.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1179.518,406)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.61,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(151,263)}夹娃娃机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(252,436)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(445.502,662)}编剧
