Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(370,410)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.17,0:01:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  有个西装革履的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, some guy in a suit
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想在开门前进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wants to come in before we open
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.29,0:01:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536,270)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.72,0:01:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个西装革履的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guy in a suit?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.87,0:01:11.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收税的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a tax collector
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.25,0:01:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐蔽好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide us, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.41,0:01:20.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快假装没事  走后门溜出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:20.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we'll walk nonchalantly to the rear exit
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.68,0:01:24.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他有张名片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:24.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got a card
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.02,0:01:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,RA小气鬼  贩卖机公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"R.A. PennyPincher Vending Supplies"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.60,0:01:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的机器到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My machine has arrived?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.44,0:01:31.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:31.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let him in
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.61,0:01:32.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它带进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:32.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it in, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  慢慢放好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, set her down easy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钥匙给你  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here are the keys, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贩卖愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy vending
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.24,0:01:40.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:40.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.17,0:01:43.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有蟹黄堡以来最伟大的摇钱树
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:43.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the greatest moneymaker since the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  这个是夹娃娃机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, meet "Skill Crane"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夹娃娃机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Skill Crane
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.45,0:01:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一次只要两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At a quarter a pop
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就能回本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this thing will pay for itself in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.77,0:01:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这倒让我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.77,0:01:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,step up, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.25,0:01:57.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一次免费
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:57.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First one's free
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.42,0:01:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:01:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thanks, I'll pass
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.51,0:02:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你肯定会想来一手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Squidward, you know you want to
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.93,0:02:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我来我就来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you insist
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.05,0:02:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.75,0:02:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去玩机器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the machine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.28,0:02:16.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:16.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, what fun
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You lose
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you see that, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我第一次差点就夹到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost got that on my first try
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的活儿完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My work here is done
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这外号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't call me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.09,0:02:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥灵巧手操大师  可不是白叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Squidward Manual- Dexterity-Tentacles" for nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我试试看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't I give it a try?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.17,0:02:37.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:37.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.87,0:02:38.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:38.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Winner
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是只小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a bear
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.80,0:02:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要叫你熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to call you Beary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.68,0:02:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新手运气好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beginner's luck
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到大佬玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's the master's turn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:56.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(554,768)}抓
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.09,0:03:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你把娃娃翻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you flipped him over
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.97,0:03:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得要不少技巧才做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That takes an awful amount of skill
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for saying so
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,熊熊说自己有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beary says he's getting lonely
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Beary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就给你夹个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get you a friend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是以为能再赢一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you think you're going to win that thing again
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.53,0:03:19.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:19.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:19.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(708,540)}你赢了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友给你吧  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go, Beary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那是帮你舒展了一下机器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I loosened that one up for you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没我的技术  你绝对赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You would have never won that without my skill
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你帮忙  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我下次玩一定会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet I win at this thing the very next time I try
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, all I've got to do is
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一次只要两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At a quarter a pop
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就能回本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this thing pays for itself in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不会信那种废话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not falling for that malarkey
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  摇摆太太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mrs. Wiggles--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,order up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,熊熊自个儿做的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beary cooked this one all by himself
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他让我好骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He makes me so proud
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid-ward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid-ward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.87,0:04:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来把这夹娃娃机解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get this over with
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.87,0:04:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need change?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You lose
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要零钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need some more change?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(266,578)}你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(694,714)}你输了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You lose
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.92,0:04:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要零钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:04:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need some change?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我已经完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because I'm all out of
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,money
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.11,0:05:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All out of
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.94,0:05:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  今天发工资
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boys, it's payday
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板  今天才星期一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Krabs, today is Monday
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.30,0:05:18.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:18.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天就是要发工资
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's payday, me boy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工资单拿去  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your check, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money, money
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.44,0:05:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我冒昧把你的工资换成了零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I took the liberty
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of turning your paycheck into quarters
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以防你想要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just in case you want to
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗衣服或者买汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do laundry or buy a soda
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,something
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真幽默  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very funny, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.35,0:05:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要是拿这两毛五还赢不到那些破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I can't win one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stupid things with this quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm walking away
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,六小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位海绵小熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBear Junior here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要我帮他赢个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wants me to win him a little brother
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才花两毛五就抓了俩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two in one quarter?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not fair
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么  皱眉小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that, Clown Frown?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.69,0:06:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你比较想坐可爱狮旁边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd rather sit next to Lovely Lion?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安顿好了  舒舒服服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, nice and cozy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看点无脑的电视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little mind-numbing television
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.42,0:06:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该就能让我忘掉那破机器了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ought to help me forget about that stupid machine
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天过得太不顺了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've had a rough day, Squiddy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.60,0:07:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过也不代表明天不会好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't mean tomorrow won't be better
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phooey
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要夹到娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to win that crane
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just once
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  拜托啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, oh, please
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让我赢一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let me win one time
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你好像有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid, I think you have a problem
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别听他的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't listen to him, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续玩下去  不赢不罢休
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you keep playing until you win
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我房子的地契
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The deed to my house
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.85,0:07:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okey-dokey, then
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carry on
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.24,0:07:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能赢一次我就不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I could just win once, I'd never play again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.65,0:08:03.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要我告诉你秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:03.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want me to tell you the secret
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮你成功夹到娃娃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of how to win on this machine?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然有秘诀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's a secret?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,secret
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你准备好要赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to be a winner?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.55,0:08:14.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:14.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.91,0:08:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:15.27,0:08:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.27,0:08:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.55,0:08:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.12,0:08:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.43,0:08:16.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:16.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  说秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, the secret
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧好吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squidward, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面对夹娃娃机  投入硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I face the crane, deposit my quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then I close my eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet, Squidward--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在与机器合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm being the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.51,0:08:33.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纯属扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:33.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's ludi
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Winner
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.16,0:08:34.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:34.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.76,0:08:35.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:35.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you try
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太离谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都闭眼了咋知道哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I close my eyes, how will I know where
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你到底想不想赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, do you want to win or not?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想赢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.27,0:08:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  投币吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, put your quarter in
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这是我最后的两毛五了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this is my last quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.58,0:08:50.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投入机器  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:50.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the machine, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.07,0:08:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与机器合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.86,0:09:02.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:02.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Winner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道我能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew I could do it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是大赢家  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a winner, aren't I?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.37,0:09:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢了赢了赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Winner, winner, winner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Winner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家看我  我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a winner, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.43,0:09:25.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:25.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点意思  据我所知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny, last time I checked
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只是个收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you were a cashier
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.30,0:09:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你怎么笑  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yuck it up all you want, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but just remember
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.97,0:09:38.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这可是在大赢家面前笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're yucking in the presence of a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽量不忘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll try to remember that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.55,0:09:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥第3498个两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,3,498 of Squidward's quarters
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥第3499个两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,3,499 of Squidward's quarters
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三层堡上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Triple-decker on deck
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别挡大赢家的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way for the winner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You lose
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没赢到奖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't win the prize?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.07,0:10:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道什么意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what that means?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.03,0:10:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.97,0:10:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没技术  注定要输
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have no skills and you're a loser
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.52,0:10:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了  看我赢的奖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a winner, see my prize
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就一输家  就只会坐着哭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a loser who sits and cries
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看见我刚刚怎么夹娃娃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you see how I handled that crane?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure did
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像是身怀绝技
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I have the magic touch
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就直接闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just closed my eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与机器合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and became the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  你厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, you're the man
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, look
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  此夹非彼夹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I don't think the same principles apply
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与机器合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与机器合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He did it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.22,0:10:56.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合二为一  合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:56.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the crane, be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你认识那位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know this guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识啊  那是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且身怀绝技
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got the magic touch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:06.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1114,732)}你的新商场
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.10,0:11:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  睁开双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, open your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合二为一  合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the crane, be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't stop
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合二为一  合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the crane, be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.40,0:11:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别合二为一  别合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't be the crane, don't be the crane
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.32,0:11:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.96,0:11:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该走了  泰迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to go, Teddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.52,0:11:53.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是想去哪呢  乱夹大师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:53.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just where do you think you're going, crane master?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪都不准去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ain't going anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.87,0:11:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持住  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,貌似我只会夹娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I can only pick up toys
