Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你来我家干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you doing in my house?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来确保你没睡过头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I came to make sure you don't oversleep
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.81,0:12:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进而误工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and miss work
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, gee, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真贴心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's very thoughtful of you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不客气  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pleasure, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好邻居就该互帮互助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what good neighbors are for
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.58,0:12:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你忽略了个小小的小细节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did overlook one teensy, little detail, however
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么细节  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.84,0:13:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好邻居不会在星期天打扰我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A good neighbor doesn't bother me on Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得章鱼哥这么暴躁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No wonder Squidward's grumpy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周日的报纸他忘了拿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He forgot his Sunday papers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就用这个向章鱼哥证明我是好邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This will show Squidward I'm a good neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.62,0:13:15.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把报纸带给他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:15.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it to him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也太重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, this is heavy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.20,0:13:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走路看路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're going
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,报纸怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A newspaper monster
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monster
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩白痴能不能行行好别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you two nincompoops kindly quiet down?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不能让他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not going to let them
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毁了我星期天剩下的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ruin the rest of my Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的星期天放松装备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My Sunday relaxation kit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:48.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1072,878)}星期天
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看  枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, pillow
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.27,0:13:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么放好  稍微垫垫脚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,placed just so for slight foot elevation
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲜花  用来点缀房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,flower to brighten the room
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,flower fragrance
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有最后一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the final touch
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我想点星期天特别服务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd like to order the Sunday special
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  上门修脚足部按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, the pedicure-and-foot-massage house call
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.47,0:14:09.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:09.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that is correct
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四点见  好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at 4:00, my good man
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天一定特别美好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be a heavenly day
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夹心糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bon-bon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:20.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(542,872)}夹心糖
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.57,0:14:23.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  天堂来的小奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:23.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello there, heaven's little wonder
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.77,0:14:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我度个巧克力假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take me on a chocolate vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全视之眼在上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the all-seeing eye
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.50,0:14:41.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你值得敬重  而我们不配
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:41.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ye are worthy, we are not
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.81,0:14:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩白痴在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you two idiots doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Secret ritual
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你举行主席就任典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To inaugurate you as president
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.07,0:14:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村主席
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,President of Bikini Bottom?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大众总算是觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew the people would come to their senses
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, silly--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是裤头村的主席
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not the president of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比那更厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even better
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.46,0:14:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:14:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.37,0:15:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是好邻居皇家密令共济会主席
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the president of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Secret Royal Order of the Good Neighbor Lodge
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.75,0:15:05.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:05.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是又胡编乱造了个什么破会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this some stupid club you two made up?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.90,0:15:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a secret
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要颁布第一道主席令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As my first presidential decree, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why don't you, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去把树叶都粉刷一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,go out and paint all the leaves on the trees
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美化附近的街区
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make the neighborhood look nicer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出去出去出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, out, out, out, out, out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.42,0:15:33.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下他们好几个星期天都有得忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:33.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll keep 'em busy for a few Sundays
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.58,0:15:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要把树叶粉刷成什么颜色  主席大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What color should we
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,paint the leaves, Your Presidentialocity?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.77,0:15:39.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刷成斑点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:39.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Polka dots
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再来烦我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, don't bother me anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斑点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Polka dots
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新主席可真天才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our new president is a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好就动手吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're ready, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要动  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold still, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快点晃我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Pat, give me a quick shake
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okey-dokey
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That worked perfectly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  好邻居派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, good neighbor Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起把整个裤头村都刷成斑点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's paint the town polka-dot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了  已经中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's already noon
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让那几个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will be darned if I let those morons
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再浪费我宝贵的星期天时光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eat up any more of my valuable Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就是好邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good neighbors are we
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on out there?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥主席好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, President Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.75,0:16:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快粉刷完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost done painting
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.37,0:16:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You poor man
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定病得不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be very sick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们送你去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let us take you to the hospital
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.00,0:17:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, really
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没事  行行好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, please
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.44,0:17:04.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:04.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm fine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天天气好  适合到乡下兜风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is a lovely day for a ride in the country
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.05,0:17:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.95,0:17:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的主席太懂生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our president sure knows how to live
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:20.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(522,748)}好邻居\N共济会
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would like to call
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.86,0:17:20.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本次好邻居共济会大会现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:20.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this meeting of the Good Neighbor Lodge to order
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先开始点名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's begin with roll call
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.97,0:17:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you home?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到他了吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you find him, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.72,0:17:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半还在兜风享受星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess he's still on his Sunday drive
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.99,0:17:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也有可能是在执行秘密任务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe he's on a secret mission
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望他没危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope he's not in danger
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.55,0:17:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Danger?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们身为好邻居共济会成员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As members of the Good Neighbor Lodge
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宣誓要保护主席免受危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we are sworn to protect our president from danger
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.04,0:17:53.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:53.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.32,0:17:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁订购了上门修脚足部按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a relaxing pedicure and foot massage
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星期天特别服务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Sunday special
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.07,0:18:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星会友  最好检查一下这位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brother Star, we better check this guy out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证他不会危害到章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make sure he's safe for Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我还有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I still have
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.99,0:18:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,日思夜想的星期天修脚服务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my Sunday pedicure to look forward to
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个在我家干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing in my house?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在做检查  要确保这位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're checking to make sure this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的是个专业修脚师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,really is a certified foot masseur
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是什么刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and not some kind of assassin
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他检查通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I say he checks out a-okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我可爱的法式甲片你见过没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, have you ever seen more lovely French tips?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法式甲片是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,French tips, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上给我来个足部放松按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make with a relaxing foot massage, pronto
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.69,0:18:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  服务时间结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, your hour's up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个  滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you two, out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想再来这里犯傻捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:45.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dragging your empty skulls around here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后半天也别来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the rest of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天也是  下周也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or tomorrow or next week
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.72,0:18:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  那算不算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, does that include
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.72,0:18:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.37,0:18:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Patrick, do you think
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥是不是话里有话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward was trying to tell us something?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还真有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们管自己叫好邻居是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You call yourselves good neighbors?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.45,0:19:06.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们纯粹就是最差邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:06.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the worst neighbors ever
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不配戴着红圆帽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't deserve to wear those fezzes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.92,0:19:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  可能真让章鱼哥主席说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Pat, maybe President Squidward's right
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.55,0:19:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.48,0:19:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到头来我们并不是好邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we aren't good neighbors after all
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来就不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you aren't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就是烂邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're horrible neighbors
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.32,0:19:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准再叫我主席
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And stop calling me president
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的星期天只剩三小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are only three hours of my Sunday left
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.95,0:19:37.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全让他们浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:37.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They took it all away
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连周日的报纸都没来得及看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't even get to read the Sunday paper
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:47.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662,972)}这是你的周日报纸  章鱼哥\N慢慢看吧  爱你的海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好邻居  我的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good neighbors, my right
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.66,0:19:55.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:55.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:20:02.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1291.302,976)}永远拦住入侵者\N全新安保系统{\fnArial}5000\N{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}免费安装
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,系统已启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,System activated
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.79,0:20:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that ought to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:22.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(694,698)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.85,0:20:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒要看看那几个傻子还怎么进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see those imbeciles try to get in here now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥主席
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,President Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.37,0:20:27.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们特此献上这个美味蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:27.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We hereby present you with this delicious cake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:30.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,854)}抱歉老是烦你\N章鱼哥
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安保系统  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Security system, help
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,入侵者警报  入侵者警报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Intruder alert, intruder alert
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,824)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,824)}未检测到威胁
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.56,0:20:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这破铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You infernal contraption
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.95,0:20:42.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非把你送回制造你的垃圾堆不可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:42.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll ship you off to the scrap heap you came from
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:42.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,766)}未检测到威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,766)}检测到威胁
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,776)}检测到威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,776)}红色警报\N红色警报
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像个嘉年华游乐设施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like a carnival ride
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for your lives
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.10,0:21:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只剩下半小时可以独处了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I only have half an hour of me-time left
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.01,0:21:25.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果我家被那俩白痴占了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:25.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the idiots took my house
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.47,0:21:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就表示那俩笨蛋不会来烦我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which means those boobs aren't around to bug me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就等着这一刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just what I've been waiting for
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.41,0:21:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算拼了老命  我都要放松
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am going to relax, if it kills me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.92,0:22:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥家在破坏附近的街区
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's house is destroying the neighborhood
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.22,0:22:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把这东西关了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.22,0:22:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to turn this thing off
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.45,0:22:04.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:04.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, not it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.62,0:22:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.77,0:22:07.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:07.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.47,0:22:10.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:10.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not it, either
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.31,0:22:16.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在星期天放松正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:16.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Sunday relaxation really hits the spot
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.52,0:22:21.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要找哪才对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:21.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:26.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(938,434)}关闭按钮
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.67,0:22:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个关闭按钮看着挺可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This "off" button seems suspicious
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.12,0:22:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功关掉了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.62,0:22:32.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥主席
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:32.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,President Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.89,0:22:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别  别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.65,0:22:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything more
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.55,0:22:38.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:38.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This was all my fault
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.92,0:22:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪我想在星期天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was the one who wanted to relax on Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻烦你们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll be so kind as to leave
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.87,0:22:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好让我准备明天上班
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can get ready for work tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.30,0:22:48.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主席大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:48.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. President
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.99,0:22:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shush
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.45,0:22:50.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们只是想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:50.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we just wanted to
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.39,0:22:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出我家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of my house
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.31,0:22:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he is
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.97,0:22:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是屋主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you the owner of this house?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.32,0:22:58.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:22:58.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.37,0:22:59.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:22:59.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.98,0:23:02.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么我代表裤头村全体居民
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:02.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then on behalf of the citizens of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.57,0:23:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你送上这张传票
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I present you with this summons
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.82,0:23:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要求赔偿你对裤头村造成的损失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to pay for the destruction of our town
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.92,0:23:11.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你下半辈子每星期天都要做社区服务
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:08.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be doing community service
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:11.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,every Sunday for the rest of your life
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.63,0:23:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你也收到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.63,0:23:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you got one of those, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.90,0:23:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这也太棒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This will be great--
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.32,0:23:19.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们三个一起清理裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:19.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the three of us cleaning up Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.18,0:23:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下周星期天再见  章鱼哥主席
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, see you next Sunday, President Squidward
